msgid "santike nibbāna vuccati. "
msgstr "you’re said to be in the presence of extinguishment. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.76, sc34
msgctxt "sn35.95:34.1"
msgid "Na so rajjati dhammesu, "
msgstr "When you know a thought with mindfulness, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:34.2"
msgid "dhammaṃ ñatvā paṭissato; "
msgstr "there’s no desire for thoughts. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:34.3"
