msgstr "you wear away, you don’t heap up: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:35.4"
msgid "Evaṃ so caratī sato; "
msgstr "that’s how to live mindfully. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:35.5"
msgid "Evaṃ apacinato dukkhaṃ, "
msgstr "Eroding suffering like this, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:35.6"
msgid "Santike nibbāna vuccatī’ti. "
msgstr "you’re said to be in the presence of extinguishment.’ "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc36
msgctxt "sn35.95:36.1"
msgid "Imassa khvāhaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāmī”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how I understand the detailed meaning of the Buddha’s brief statement.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.95:36.2"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, mālukyaputta. "
msgstr "“Good, good, Māluṅkyaputta! "

msgctxt "sn35.95:36.3"
msgid "Sādhu kho tvaṃ, mālukyaputta, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāsi: "
msgstr "It’s good that you understand the detailed meaning of what I’ve said in brief like this. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc37
msgctxt "sn35.95:37.1"
msgid "‘Rūpaṃ disvā sati muṭṭhā, "
msgstr "(The Buddha repeats the verses in full.) "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:37.2"
msgid "Piyaṃ nimittaṃ manasi karoto; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:37.3"
msgid "Sārattacitto vedeti, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:37.4"
msgid "Tañca ajjhosa tiṭṭhati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc38
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.1"
msgid "Tassa vaḍḍhanti vedanā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.2"
msgid "anekā rūpasambhavā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.3"
msgid "Abhijjhā ca vihesā ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.4"
msgid "cittamassūpahaññati; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.5"
msgid "Evaṃ ācinato dukkhaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.6"
msgid "ārā nibbāna vuccati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.95:38.7"
msgid "… pe … "
msgstr " "

