#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc41
msgctxt "sn35.95:41.1"
msgid "Imassa kho, mālukyaputta, mayā saṅkhittena bhāsitassa evaṃ vitthārena attho daṭṭhabbo”ti. "
msgstr "This is how to understand the detailed meaning of what I said in brief.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc42
msgctxt "sn35.95:42.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mālukyaputto bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinanditvā anumoditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi. "
msgstr "And then Venerable Māluṅkyaputta approved and agreed with what the Buddha said. He got up from his seat, bowed, and respectfully circled the Buddha, keeping him on his right, before leaving. "

msgctxt "sn35.95:42.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mālukyaputto eko vūpakaṭṭho appamatto ātāpī pahitatto viharanto nacirasseva—yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihāsi. "
msgstr "Then Māluṅkyaputta, living alone, withdrawn, diligent, keen, and resolute, soon realized the supreme end of the spiritual path in this very life. He lived having achieved with his own insight the goal for which gentlemen rightly go forth from the lay life to homelessness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.95:42.3"
msgid "“Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā”ti abbhaññāsi. "
msgstr "He understood: “Rebirth is ended; the spiritual journey has been completed; what had to be done has been done; there is no return to any state of existence.” "

msgctxt "sn35.95:42.4"
msgid "Aññataro ca panāyasmā mālukyaputto arahataṃ ahosīti. "
msgstr "And Venerable Māluṅkyaputta became one of the perfected. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.95:42.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

